                            "#tail": ", you can view the different ways he or she has been involved in various cases. For example, you can view charts that show which parties retained the expert witness and how the cases were resolved, cite lists that describe the outcome of each case, opinions issued by judges associated with the case, and so forth."
                        },
                        "#text": "While viewing a particular expert witness using"
